    # game/areas/howlerslair.rpy:43
    old "You’re more used to {color=#f6d6bd}[horsename]’s{/color} trot than to your own gait. You rush forward as if you’re tracking your next meal, or delivering a message. \n\nAfter a few minutes, the light dancing on the calm surface of the lake lures your eyes, and the whispering meadow calms down your breath.[deafcustom1] "
    new ""

